title: Fix db migration after key/value restore
message:
Fix db migration after key/value restore

When user was using app ver 20 and key/value backup was made (API < 23), re-installing the app to newer version caused db file to be replaced without applying db migration. This change does db migration on backup data by closing and re-opening db helper which will be notice that schema version was changed.
